Remake of Donkey.bas

---
-----------------



This is a remake of the Donkey.bas game shipped with early versions of PC-DOS and MS-DOS using Ruby and Chingu game programming library.



Chingu game library available from:
	http://ippa.se/chingu



Car sprite originally lifted from:

	http://s961.beta.photobucket.com/user/Maxie012/media/Huh/racecars.png.html





Donkey sprite originally lifted from:

	http://yo-yomaster.deviantart.com/art/Evolution-of-a-donkey-sprite-72039588





Road graphic is an original created by me.





Feel free to do whatever you want with this quick'n'dirty, ugly, poorly-written Ruby code.
